<ab facs="#facs_201_r1l20">vnd Annen vnd Kathrein <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Kornerin <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> cʒüm hofe / Darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_201_r1l21"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vvıllen beſant vnd cʒe rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_201_r1l22">geſacʒt / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ ſich die ſache langcʒeit vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_201_r1l23">gehandelt hab ee Jr do Amptman <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeit / vnd er 
<del rend="strikethrough"> hab </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_201_line_1576594442281_8433">hab </ab></add> ſeinen <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
